sp_chrome_https_case_text.message: This extension cannot make suggestions from pages like this which have secure content (e.g. https://). See you back on the public web!

sp_chrome_special_case_text.message:
This extension works best on homepages or the main page of most websites.

Try the extension on a website that you already love—, test-drive it and see the page suggestions about something you know.

sp_description.message: Discover web pages similar to the page that you're currently browsing.

sp_domain_change_message.message: To change your local domain to www.google.co.uk, click here.

sp_domain_clicked_message.message: www.google.com has been saved as your local domain for retrieving similar pages.

sp_domain_message.message: The extension will contact $1 to retrieve the list of similar pages.

sp_options_feedback.message: We'd love to hear any feedback that you have at similarpages-extension@google.com. Thanks!

sp_options_intro.message: The Google Similar Pages browser extension allows you quickly to preview and explore other pages that are similar to the one that you are browsing - on the fly!

sp_options_legal.message:
When you click the Similar Pages button, your browser will send a search query to Google to see if there are any similar pages for the page that you are viewing.

The data related to the query will be handled as described in Google's privacy policy

sp_options_uninstall_message.message: To uninstall Google Similar Pages, use Chrome's Tools > Extensions menu option and click the Uninstall link for the Google Similar Pages extension.

sp_tld_special_case_text.message: The extension is currently not available for your country/region. Please check again soon.
